text:
First-place votes in parentheses

Coaches voting: Rich Angarano , Brookfield; Tom Brockett , Ansonia; Jim Buonocore , Ledyard; Craig Bruno , Naugatuck; Scott Daniels , Glastonbury; Joe DellaVecchia , St. Joseph; Steve Filippone , Hand; Rob Fleeting, Windsor; Steve George , Newtown; Tanner Grove, Montville; Tim King, Valley Regional/Old Lyme; Sean Marinan, Xavier; Marce Petroccio , Staples. 
COMING EVENTS 
ABBOTT TECH: The Abbott Tech baseball team’s free youth clinic and the Danbury Youth Baseball food drive have been rescheduled to Oct. 18 at Rogers Park. The clinic will begin at 4:30 p.m. and is open to players ages 10-12. It will be conducted by Abbott Tech head coach Dave Simone and his players. To register, visit DanburyYouthBaseball.com. All players who participate in the clinic are asked to donate at least one can of food to the food drive.
